Title: ASP.NET Social Bookmarks
Description: Simple and extensible Web User Control for ASP.NET that supports various social networks (Twitter, Facebook, Google Bookmarks, etc)
HomeWiki:
Project Description
Simple and extensible Web User Control for ASP.NET that supports various social networks (Twitter, Facebook, Google Bookmarks, etc)

By default you can use this social networks:

- Twitter
- Facebook
- Google Bookmarks
- Picasa
- RSS Feeds
- Flickr
- E-mail
- Linkedin
- Maps

You can easily add new custom components to the control.

More info available at http://blastersystems.com/blog/?p=221 (Translation available at the right toolbar )
